						<li>
							<a href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AThe Canoe in the Forest%0D%0AAn unfinished boat hidden on a remote island in Alaska illuminates a missing chapter in the history of traditional Haida and Tlingit canoe building%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/features/the-canoe-in-the-forest/" title="Share by Email" target="_blank">
